Albert Frederick THYBOE et al., Plaintiffs, Appellants, v. SAN JUAN FRUIT CO. et al., Defendants, Appellees. Circuit Court of Appeals, First Circuit. May 25, 1928. No. 2240.

Before BINGHAM, JOHNSON, and ANDERSON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

It is ordered that this case he, and the same hereby is, dismissed.
